snippet: Sky, a 5-year-old wire fox terrier, won the top crown at the 138th Westminster Kennel Club Dog Show on Tuesday, becoming the 14th member of her breed to win best in show.
abstract: Wire fox terrier Sky wins Best in Show at the 138th Westminster Kennel Club Dog Show, giving breed its 14th historical victory; veteran terrier edges out bloodhound Nathan, the crowd favorite.
lead_paragraph: Sky, a 5-year-old wire fox terrier, won the top crown at the 138th Westminster Kennel Club Dog Show on Tuesday, becoming the 14th member of her breed to win best in show.

headline.main: Sky, Wire Fox Terrier and Veteran Show Dog, Wins at Westminster
headline.print_headline: Sky, Wire Fox Terrier and Veteran Show Dog, Wins at Westminster
